             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a labouring man; I saw the prisoner go up stairs, in the prosecutor's house; I saw him come down; and I told the prosecutor; I saw the prisoner go out of the house, and I saw him taken.</p>
               <p>CHARLES FOX sworn.</p>
               <p>I saw the prisoner taken; and three watches and two watch cases were taken from him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17891028-1-person50">
