             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a constable; I produce the watches and cases, which I took out of the prisoner's pocket, and have kept them ever since.</p>
               <p>(Deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have nothing to say.</p>
               <p>
            
